# AI Provider API Keys (optional - only set what you need)
# Ollama runs locally and needs no key. It is the default provider.

# OpenAI - get your key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Gaia - get your key at https://gaianet.ai
# GAIA_API_KEY=gaia-...

# AIsa.one - get your key at https://aisa.one
# AISA_API_KEY=asi-...
